I"R<h1 id="openproject-903">OpenProject 9.0.3</h1>

<p>We released <a href="https://community.openproject.com/versions/1376">OpenProject 9.0.3</a>.
The release contains several bug fixes and we recommend updating to the newest version.</p>

<h4 id="bug-fixes-and-changes">Bug fixes and changes</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Changed: Searching for Custom Fields [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/29756">#29756</a>]</li>
  <li>Changed: Prevent collisions between users working on the same board [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30403">#30403</a>]</li>
  <li>Changed: Do not send email notifications for changes in child work packages [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30532">#30532</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Version field flickers [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30356">#30356</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Missing translations for boards [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30367">#30367</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Work package description not updated after initial edit [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30373">#30373</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Parent work package in Gantt chart not displayed correctly [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30388">#30388</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Cannot delete date from work packages of a type that is a milestone [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30390">#30390</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Work packages in closed version suggest status editable but then nothing happens [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30396">#30396</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Wrong language is displayed in some date fields [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30400">#30400</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Project Paisy: Connecting functional document fails without error message [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30404">#30404</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Button Release to production not visible for Releasemanager [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30405">#30405</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Text references to SVN revisions don’t create links [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30415">#30415</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: User with :manage_boards but without :manage_public_queries can create faulty board columns [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30426">#30426</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Tag shown on My page for time tracking comments [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30432">#30432</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: [Error 500] An error occurred on the page you were trying to access [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30435">#30435</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: OmniAuth login link in top menu not styled properly. [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30436">#30436</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Board list not sorted alphabetically [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30444">#30444</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Not all multiples of 4096 bytes are folders [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30450">#30450</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Search work package hints are not links [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30457">#30457</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: New API-backed attachments always use content disposition attachment [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30492">#30492</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Can not switch to hierarchy mode in work packages list [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30514">#30514</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Error when copying a work package [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30518">#30518</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Gantt chart: Jump when scheduling finish date of work package with only start date [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30554">#30554</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Comma and dot flipped for values in cost report and budgets (German language setting) [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30574">#30574</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Inline-create useless when only add_work_packages_permission present [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30589">#30589</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Cannot close Arbeitspaket [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30590">#30590</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: “Login” instead of “Login name” used (causes problems with translations) [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30591">#30591</a>]</li>
  <li>Fixed: Board links in sidebar broken [<a href="https://community.openproject.com/wp/30595">#30595</a>]</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="contributions">Contributions</h4>

<p>A big thanks to community members for reporting bugs and helping us identifying and providing fixes.</p>

